  "prompt": "What are some best hotel in Jaipur?",
  "response": "Jaipur, also known as the \"Pink City,\" is a popular tourist destination with a wide range of accommodation options.\n\n1. **The Oberoi Rajvilas**:\n   - A luxury resort offering elegant rooms, villas, and tents in a sprawling, landscaped garden setting.\n   - Renowned for its impeccable service and tranquil environment.\n\n2. **Rambagh Palace**:\n   - A stunning property managed by Taj Hotels, formerly the residence of Jaipur's royalty.\n   - Offers opulent rooms and suites, as well as exceptional dining and spa services.\n\n3. **Le M\u00e9ridien Jaipur Resort & Spa**:\n   - Offers a mix of modern design and traditional Rajasthani decor.\n   - Features spacious rooms, a spa, and multiple dining options.\n\n4. **Fairmont Jaipur**:\n   - Known for its grand architecture inspired by Mughal and Rajput traditions.\n   - Features luxury rooms, fine dining, and excellent event facilities.\n\n5. **Samode Haveli**:\n   - A heritage hotel that offers a blend of traditional charm and modern comforts.\n   - Known for its personalized service and beautiful courtyards.\n\n6. **Trident Jaipur**:\n   - Overlooking the Mansagar Lake and the Jal Mahal, it offers comfortable rooms and beautiful views.\n   - Known for its excellent service and family-friendly atmosphere.\n\n7. **Jaipur Marriott Hotel**:\n   - Offers contemporary accommodations with a full range of modern amenities.\n   - Features multiple dining options and a relaxing spa.\n\n8. **ITC Rajputana**:\n   - A luxury hotel designed with Rajasthani architectural influences.\n   - Offers refined rooms, excellent dining options, and a relaxing spa.\n\nWhether you're looking for opulence, heritage, or modern comforts, Jaipur has a hotel to suit your needs.",
